			<h1>About Us!</h1>
		<div  id='textbody'>
			<p>Hello! Welcome to The Weird Side of YouTube! We are an open-source project started by members of Alpha Chi Rho fraternity at Rensselaer Polytechnic Institute in Troy New York. If you're an avid fan of random and wierd Youtube videos, you're at the right place.
			<br>
			<br>
			The current team is comprised of Mike Metrocavich, Colin Atkinson, Jacob Lane, Nathan Siviy, YoungChul Chun, James Lee. 
			<br>
			Past members include Erik Baktis, Matt Zielinski, Jake Martin, Ashwin Raghuraman, and Alex Metrocavich.	
			<br>
			<br>
			If you would like to learn more about RCOS at RPI or any of the oher active projects, visit
		<a href="https://rcos.io">our web page.</a></p>
		</div>
